    f_\hi(\st, \act) & \approx f(\bar {\st}^i_\hi, \bar {\act}^i_\hi) + \nabla_{\st } f(\bar {\st}^i_\hi, \bar {\act}^i_\hi)(\st - \bar {\st}^i_\hi) + \nabla_{\act } f(\bar {\st}^i_\hi, \bar {\act}^i_\hi)(\act - \bar {\act}^i_\hi)                         \\
